{"tid":500851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【政情】議事規則戰　泛民與逆轉勝擦身而過 [369]","createTime":"2017-12-16T08:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T08:45:36.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d5995963c982db72c40dcdde9f0a2ae33517c1","tid":500851,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:20:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】議事規則攻防戰，主席梁君彥在聖誕前完成審議的願望達成。<br />\n<br />\n建制派一直刻意減少發言，迫使民主派用盡發言時間。最後一顆子彈鄺俊宇周五一開會就已完成發言，會議節奏已由建制派掌控。<br />\n<br />\n民主派晚上舉行集會，為免被群眾包圍，建制派最理想是在傍晚前表決。「班長」廖長江早就呼籲建制派各黨由代表發言，期望盡快完成。<br />\n<br />\n不過，連日讓路民主派發言，不少建制派都心中有氣。這一刻都要爆了，相繼發言到接近中午，心知再不停口就未必能即日表決，據聞原本按掣發言的自由黨邵家輝都臨時取消。<br />\n<br />\n泛民主派沒有空間動口就只能動手，期望透過激烈示威迫使主席梁君彥休會，甚至轉房開會拖延更多時間。朱凱廸、陳志全出動鎖鏈將自己綁在凳上，怎料保安人員一早準備大剪刀，將「苦肉計」瞬間擊破。多名議員陸續起哄被抬走，會議廳內反而越來越平靜迎接表決一刻。<br />\n<br />\n上次會議一同衝出主席台的泛民主派議員今次各有行動。《政情》聽聞部分議員認為除了以口號說「不」，亦有必要立此存照，留在議事廳投反對票。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不過，天意往往弄人，泛民機關算盡，但其實若他們全部乖乖投票，建制派的建議就未必會通過，因為民建聯陳克勤稱機器故障投了反對票</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，若泛民齊人投票，地區直選組別票數會與建制相同，到時打和，泛民就真的可以叫SUPER。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab3dec3d1bb5c6508a015aa7518e1e342222544","tid":500851,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2227c9506ab5edcbda241b6a4d5ff0133c971fc","tid":500851,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45a536953032e7bfe3c3aca5ad0ae8630a06a95","tid":500851,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:28:31.000Z","msg":"嘥氣啦<br />\n大口狗可以話機器故障投票無效<br />\n再投過泛民都係輸"},{"pid":"3cc687821cf2a9cdfe1798099bdbb2091c250996","tid":500851,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"大家都做馬騮戲，認真你就輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2e2cd5c67abea7904f5f392e6f439c31a67016","tid":500851,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘥氣啦<br />\n大口狗可以話機器故障投票無效<br />\n再投過泛民都係輸</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf280359cb84c64a4500de530f7fd564bf94994","tid":500851,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"歷史在笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a175a5cf1df2169024b547e726ae7371dc0fb17","tid":500851,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"Now 新聞👍"}]}